of these three headline

00:47:32.480 --> 00:47:35.850
approaches-- So if you
can take one and pass

00:47:35.850 --> 00:47:39.610
them along-- and also
a section to write down

00:47:39.610 --> 00:47:42.660
the keywords that you
own or want to own.

00:47:42.660 --> 00:47:44.400
So take one and pass them down.

