I've got some extra ones here.

00:47:56.280 --> 00:48:02.520
So look at what
your keywords are.

00:48:02.520 --> 00:48:09.470
And when you're thinking of
keywords, try to be expansive.

00:48:09.470 --> 00:48:14.170
So have as many keywords that
might be useful for your brand.

00:48:14.170 --> 00:48:17.574
This is just page one
we're going to look at.

00:48:17.574 --> 00:48:19.490
And so the first thing
you want to think about

00:48:19.490 --> 00:48:26.610
is this section number
two, the keyword headline,

00:48:26.610 --> 00:48:29.520
the power statement,
the hybrid headline.

00:48:29.520 --> 00:48:33.490
And the headline on
a LinkedIn profile

00:48:33.490 --> 00:48:36.050
is very similar to a tweet.

00:48:36.050 --> 00:48:41.560
It's 140 characters, roughly,
so it's like a long sentence.

00:48:41.560 --> 00:48:45.850
So explore what would
work best for you.

00:48:45.850 --> 00:48:48.610
How can you improve
your LinkedIn headline

00:48:48.610 --> 00:48:51.970
so that it's a stronger
statement about who you are?

00:48:51.970 --> 00:48:54.580
And some people
add some elements

00:48:54.580 --> 00:48:56.830
to it that are interesting,
like humanitarian

00:48:56.830 --> 00:49:00.150
at the end or something like
that, that dimensionalizes them

00:49:00.150 --> 00:49:01.070
in a different way.

00:49:01.070 --> 00:49:04.450
So you want to look for ways
to stand out and be different.

00:49:04.450 --> 00:49:06.950
So let's focus just
on page one here,

00:49:06.950 --> 00:49:10.850
defining who your
target audience is.

00:49:10.850 --> 00:49:16.390
And I want you to look at it a
little bit as a psychographic

00:49:16.390 --> 00:49:20.060
of your audience, so not
just certain kinds of people

00:49:20.060 --> 00:49:21.070
you're pitching.

00:49:21.070 --> 00:49:22.730
You can define them
in job function.

00:49:22.730 --> 00:49:24.600
But also what's their mindset?

00:49:24.600 --> 00:49:26.340
What's on their mind?

00:49:26.340 --> 00:49:30.230
And then put together
your headline

00:49:30.230 --> 00:49:33.750
that would most appeal
to that target audience.

