00:59:42.650 --> 00:59:45.230
And as I say, super sellers,
they're kind of divided down

00:59:45.230 --> 00:59:49.570
the middle from people who only
build a network that's really

00:59:49.570 --> 00:59:51.480
what I'd call genuine, i.e.

00:59:51.480 --> 00:59:54.480
people that they know, whereas
