This is a client's
story of, again,

02:07:06.520 --> 02:07:12.610
branching out into areas
outside the IT department

02:07:12.610 --> 02:07:16.030
for building business
and companies.

02:07:16.030 --> 02:07:18.390
So the whole idea was
finding business leaders

02:07:18.390 --> 02:07:23.010
